node.text: Here are the mf new nails.

Happy Monday! A little BTS from last week before this epic shot. I love working with my team. They are really amazing. I went to hot yoga this morning & just took my vitamins for the day. I'm off to a great start. Let's get it! I'm taking the next two weeks to workout every single day so send me some good vibes. Im already one week down 💪🏾
